irmingham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Birmingham\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his other mini mascots\", \"from\": 409, \"to\": 431}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 525, \"to\": 533}, {\"ngram\": \"their kit\", \"from\": 542, \"to\": 551}, {\"ngram\": \"local team announcements\", \"from\": 571, \"to\": 595}, {\"ngram\": \"fan zones\", \"from\": 617, \"to\": 626}, {\"ngram\": \"the action\", \"from\": 636, \"to\": 646}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am very excited as only six people will get to be a mini mascot for the Paris Olympics,\\\" Josh said.\", \"from\": 653, \"to\": 755, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 745, \"end\": 749, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.9892087824480801, \"rank\": 0.01072357214038749, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"only six people\", \"from\": 675, \"to\": 690}, {\"ngram\": \"a mini mascot\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 719}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 742}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He added: \\\"It feels even more special because I am the only mascot fromScotland.\\\"\", \"from\": 757, \"to\": 838, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the only mascot fromScotland\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 836}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Josh's dad, Mark Davidson, added: \\\"He's buzzing, and he actually found out a couple of months ago, so he has done really well not mentioning it.\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 984, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 840, \"end\": 844, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.9892087824480801, \"rank\": 0.01072357214038749, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}, {\"begin\": 852, \"end\": 865, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.