ool role\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1307}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Well, it all began with a ballot and a random selection process.\", \"from\": 1310, \"to\": 1374, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a ballot\", \"from\": 1334, \"to\": 1342}, {\"ngram\": \"a random selection process\", \"from\": 1347, \"to\": 1373}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mark explained: \\\"Angela (Josh's mum and Mark's wife) applied to a ballot around Autumn last year, which was open to all kids in the UK aged between like five and 11 or 12.\", \"from\": 1380, \"to\": 1551, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1405, \"end\": 1409, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.9892087824480801, \"rank\": 0.01072357214038749, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}, {\"begin\": 1512, \"end\": 1514, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999826461549347, \"rank\": 1.7354039522997668e-05, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mark\", \"from\": 1380, \"to\": 1384}, {\"ngram\": \"Angela\", \"from\": 1397, \"to\": 1403}, {\"ngram\": \"Mark's wife\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1431}, {\"ngram\": \"a ballot\", \"from\": 1444, \"to\": 1452}, {\"ngram\": \"Autumn\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1466}, {\"ngram\": \"all kids\", \"from\": 1496, \"to\": 1504}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"From that, 40 kids were selected at random - one of which was Josh.\", \"from\": 1553, \"to\": 1621, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1616, \"end\": 1620, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.9892087824480801, \"rank\": 0.01072357214038749, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"40 kids\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1572}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We then had to submit a video on why he should be picked as a mini mascot and his reasons for wanting to be involved in the process as well as hishistorywith sport.\\\"\", \"from\": 1623, \"to\": 1789, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a video\", \"from\": 1646, \"to\": 1653}, {\"ngram\": \"a mini mascot\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1697}, {\"ngram\": \"his reasons\", \"from\": 1702, \"to\": 1713}, {\"ngram\": \"the process\", \"from\": 1744, \"to\": 1755}, {\"ngram\": \"hishistorywith sport\", \"from\": 1767, \"to\": 1787}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And Josh's history with sport is certainly an incredible one.\", \"from\": 1791, \"to\": 1852, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1795, \"end\": 1799, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.9892087824480801, \"rank\": 0.01072357214038749, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1815, \"to\": 1820}, {\"ngram\": \"an incredible one\", \"from\": 1834, \"to\": 1851}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having started Taekwondo classes at the age of three, the youngster quickly grew into somewhat of a superstar in the popular martial art form.\", \"from\": 1856, \"to\": 1998, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Taekwondo classes\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1888}, {\"ngram\": \"the age\", \"from\": 1892, \"to\": 1899}, {\"ngram\": \"the youngster\", \"from\": 1910, \"to\": 1923}, {\"ngram\": \"a superstar\", \"from\": 1954, \"to\": 1965}, {\"ngram\": \"the popular martial art form\", \"from\": 1969, \"to\": 1997}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With his blue belt now in the bag, the school pupil has travelled all over theworldwinning trophies and medals as well as making a name for himself.\", \"from\": 2000, \"to\": 2148, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his blue belt\", \"from\": 2005, \"to\": 2018}, {\"ngram\": \"the bag\", \"from\": 2026, \"to\": 2033}, {\"ngram\": \"the school pupil\", \"from\": 2035, \"to\": 2051}, {\"ngram\": \"trophies\", \"from\": 2091, \"to\": 2099}, {\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 2104, \"to\": 2110}, {\"ngram\": \"a name\", \"from\": 2129, \"to\": 2135}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mark said: \\\"We are really proud of what he has achieved at such a young age.\", \"from\": 2150, \"to\": 2226, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mark\", \"from\": 2150, \"to\": 2154}, {\"ngram\": \"such a young age\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2225}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He trains three to four times a week and competes nationally between four and six times a year and internationally once a year.\", \"from\": 2228, \"to\": 2356, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"competes\", \"from\": 2270, \"to\": 2278}, {\"ngram\": \"four and six times\", \"from\": 2298, \"to\": 2316}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He just performed at the Dutch Open in Holland and won a silver medal in the under-12s category.\", \"from\": 2358, \"to\": 2455, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2398, \"end\": 2405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9930590505371862, \"rank\": 0.005297046183640896, \"text\": \"Holland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Dutch Open\", \"from\": 2380, \"to\": 2394}, {\"ngram\": \"a silver medal\", \"from\": 2414, \"to\": 2428}, {\"ngram\": \"the under-12s category\", \"from\": 2432, \"to\": 2454}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He has such an incredible passion for the sport, and he wants to be the best in the country.\", \"from\": 2457, \"to\": 2550, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such an incredible passion\", \"from\": 2465, \"to\": 2491}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 2496, \"to\": 2505}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 2538, \"to\": 2549}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are so proud to support him.\\\"\", \"from\": 2550, \"to\": 2583, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Josh added: \\\"I love competing and meeting new people and keeping fit.\", \"from\": 2587, \"to\": 2656, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2587, \"end\": 2591, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.9892087824480801, \"rank\": 0.01072357214038749, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"new people\", \"from\": 2629, \"to\": 2639}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I also enjoy learning new skills when I am training.\\\"\", \"from\": 2656, \"to\": 2710, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"new skills\", \"from\": 2679, \"to\": 2689}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2024 Paris Olympic Summer Games will take place between July 26 and August 11.\", \"from\": 2712, \"to\": 2794, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 2024 Paris Olympic Summer Games\", \"from\": 2712, \"to\": 2747}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 2758, \"to\": 2763}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 2772, \"to\": 2776}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 2784, \"to\": 2790}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For more information, clickHERE This website and associated newspapers adhere to the Independent Press Standards Organisation's Editors' Code of Practice.\", \"from\": 2796, \"to\": 2955, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more information\", \"from\": 2800, \"to\": 2816}, {\"ngram\": \"clickHERE\", \"from\": 2818, \"to\": 2827}, {\"ngram\": \"This website\", \"from\": 2828, \"to\": 2840}, {\"ngram\": \"associated newspapers\", \"from\": 2845, \"to\": 2866}, {\"ngram\": \"the Independent Press Standards Organisation's Editors' Code\", \"f